18.819048 0 0 1-105.618286 187.684571l-33.889523-65.097143a145.700571 145.700571 0 0 0 66.364952-122.563047c0-47.957333-22.918095-90.453333-58.221714-116.906667l52.077714-52.077714z m-112.956952-152.868572v24.478477L127.73181 713.386667a73.142857 73.142857 0 0 1-41.569524-65.999238V403.407238a73.142857 73.142857 0 0 1 68.827428-73.020952l4.924953-0.121905 197.680762 3.291429 157.915428-166.229334c34.474667-36.327619 96.060952-12.117333 96.060953 37.741714z'></path></svg></div><div class='live-badge top-left'>Live</div><div class='live-loading'></div><div class='live-error-placeholder'><svg t='1776112172334' class='icon' viewBox='0 0 1024 1024' version='1.1' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' p-id='8506' width='200' height='200'><path d='M512 97.52381c228.912762 0 414.47619 185.563429 414.47619 414.47619s-185.563429 414.47619-414.47619 414.47619S97.52381 740.912762 97.52381 512 283.087238 97.52381 512 97.52381z m0 73.142857C323.486476 170.666667 170.666667 323.486476 170.666667 512s152.81981 341.333333 341.333333 341.333333 341.333333-152.81981 341.333333-341.333333S700.513524 170.666667 512 170.666667z m-191.488 486.521904c134.436571-93.037714 248.539429-93.037714 382.976 0l-41.642667 60.14781c-109.372952-75.727238-190.317714-75.727238-299.690666 0zM414.47619 341.333333a48.761905 48.761905 0 0 1 48.761905 48.761905v73.142857a48.761905 48.761905 0 1 1-97.523809 0v-73.142857a48.761905 48.761905 0 0 1 48.761904-48.761905z m195.04762 0a48.761905 48.761905 0 0 1 48.761904 48.761905v73.142857a48.761905 48.761905 0 1 1-97.523809 0v-73.142857a48.761905 48.761905 0 0 1 48.761905-48.761905z' p-id='8507'></path></svg></div></div><div class='live-caption'>循环播放的动图 Loop-Playing Live Photo</div>  \n<p>开启循环播放后，小猫的动态会一直重复展示，非常适合用来突出可爱的小动作，让画面更生动有趣。</p>\n<p>With loop playback enabled, the kitten’s movement will repeat continuously, which is perfect for highlighting cute little actions and making the scene more vivid and interesting.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>有时候我们不需要固定宽度，而是希望通过高度来控制整体比例，让动态图片在页面中更协调。</p>\n<p>Sometimes we don’t need a fixed width; instead, we want to control the overall ratio by height to make the live photo more coordinated on the page.</p>\n<div class='live-photo-container' style=\"height:200px; width:fit-content;\"><img src=\"/image/loading.gif\" data-lazy-src=\"https://cdn.gallery.uuanqin.top/live_photo/cover/ezgif-5901921d3f722129260414.jpg\" alt='Live Photo' class='live-photo-static' style='height:200px; width:auto; max-width:100%; object-fit:contain; opacity: 1;'><video muted playsinline autoplay loop preload='auto' class='live-photo-video' src='https://cdn.gallery.uuanqin.top/live_photo/video/ezgif-5901921d3f722129260414.mp4' style='height:200px; width:auto; max-width:100%; object-fit:contain;'></video><div class='live-sound-toggle' title='Sound Toggle'><svg class='sound-on-icon' viewBox='0 0 1024 1024' width='15' height='15' fill='currentColor'><path d='M949.418667 502.369524v64.024381c-10.800762 120.539429-82.115048 223.646476-183.344762 278.723047L732.330667 780.190476A280.30781 280.30781 0 0 0 877.714286 534.381714a280.380952 280.380952 0 0 0-153.941334-250.319238l33.694477-64.926476c105.764571 53.808762 180.833524 159.305143 191.951238 283.233524z m-145.627429 24.576a218.819048 218.819048 0 0 1-105.618286 187.66019l-33.889523-65.097143a145.700571 145.700571 0 0 0 66.364952-122.563047 145.700571 145.700571 0 0 0-68.583619-124.001524l33.792-65.048381a218.819048 218.819048 0 0 1 107.934476 189.049905zM611.547429 205.04381V829.19619c0 49.859048-61.561905 74.044952-96.060953 37.741715l-160.353524-146.383238H159.305143a73.142857 73.142857 0 0 1-73.142857-73.142857V403.407238a73.142857 73.142857 0 0 1 68.827428-73.020952l4.924953-0.121905 197.680762 3.291429 157.915428-166.229334c34.474667-36.327619 96.060952-12.117333 96.060953 37.741714z'></path></svg><svg class='sound-off-icon' viewBox='0 0 1024 1024' width='15' height='15' fill='currentColor'><path d='M611.547429 470.918095v358.253715c0 49.859048-61.561905 74.044952-96.060953 37